**:loudspeaker: AnZo-notify – Sleek & Stylish Notification System for QB-Core**
`Level up your FiveM server’s user experience with AnZo-notify, a modern and customizable notification system designed for QB-Core. Built with performance and aesthetics in mind, AnZo-notify delivers clean, animated alerts for player actions, system messages, and server events.`

> :sparkles: Features:
> :white_check_mark: Stylish UI inspired by modern design trends
> :white_check_mark: Fully customizable colors, icons & animations
> :white_check_mark: Supports client & server-side triggers
> :white_check_mark: Lightweight & optimized for performance
> :white_check_mark: Seamless integration with QB-Core framework
